name: Omniscient
overview: In a city where citizens are monitored 24/7, a tech employee must outsmart her surveillance drone in order to investigate a murder.

episodes.name: I committed a crime
episodes.overview: After her dad is murdered, tech trainee Nina risks everything to find out why the Omniscient surveillance system's drones failed to monitor his killer.

episodes.name: A good person who's done a horrible thing
episodes.overview: As Nina investigates her father's past, she finds an ally in Judite, a city hall worker. Outside the surveillance zone, Daniel gets into trouble.

episodes.name: This is our Pandora's Box
episodes.overview: As trainees prepare for their final assessment, Nina gets ready to use ruthless tactics to secure a permanent spot. Vinícius grows closer to Nina.

episodes.name: Who wants to dive in first?
episodes.overview: Judite takes a big risk to help Nina. Vinícius considers a key career move. At group therapy with Vinícius, Nina involuntarily opens up.

episodes.name: Open this door!
episodes.overview: Daniel attends Inácio's funeral. Nina exploits a system vulnerability to break into Omniscient. Suspicious of Nina, Vinícius considers his next move.
